This is a simple ansible playbook that collects some information from the system adn create a small report from it.

- The Script contains two files "get_report.yml" and "get_report.j2"
- The result of those scripts will be txt file with the name "Final_Report.txt"
- To execute the script use the following command:
     - ansible-playbook get_report.yml

- the output file contains the following information:
    - Disk usage
    - Real Memory usage
    - Swap space Usage
    - CPU Load
    - Running services
    - SELinux status and configuration
    - Network Service status
    - Nework interfaces status and configuartion
    - Open Ports 
    - DNS system Configuration
    - DNS system status
    - Routing table
    - Firewall Rules

